":"sterilised sealable jar, frying pan, pastry brush, serving platter, refrigerator, stove top","hintsAndTricks":["You can replace the red chillies with green chillies in this recipe, if desired.","You can replace the palm sugar with brown sugar in this recipe, if desired.","Chilli jam can be stored in a sealable jar for up to 2 weeks in the refrigerator."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","25m","10 portions"]}